NT_gaussian_rnd_dist_o Class Reference

NT_gaussian_rnd_dist_o returns values out of a gaussian random distribution objects based upon inidividual paramters for each subspace Idea : The usage idea is to call the object which returns a NTreal or NT_vector_o containing random values out of its specific distribution [a,b].

#include <nt_gaussian_rnd_dist_obj.h>
